# Common Agent Guidelines

Use `AGENTS.md` as the project instruction entry point.

Shared rules live in `docs/agent-guidelines/`. When adding or changing a
persistent project rule, update the canonical guideline first. Keep Cursor rules
as lightweight adapters for metadata, globs, and pointers only.

Before working in an area covered by `AGENTS.md` or the Rule Index, read the
relevant guideline file and follow it for the task.
